tags.name: elmsln-loading
tags.description:
`elmsln-loading`
A spinner to tell the user that something is loading.
This is just the spinner though and doesn't provide any text or anything else.

Attributes:

  * `color` {`string`} - color

  * `size` {`string`} - tiny, small, medium, large, epic sizing.

  * `accent-color` {`string`} - a selected accent-"color": grey, red, pink, purple, etc.

  * `dark` {`boolean`} - make the default theme dark?

  * `colors` - make the default theme dark?

Properties:

  * `color` {`string`} - color

  * `size` {`string`} - tiny, small, medium, large, epic sizing.

  * `accentColor` {`string`} - a selected accent-"color": grey, red, pink, purple, etc.

  * `dark` {`boolean`} - make the default theme dark?

  * `__utils` - 

  * `colors` - make the default theme dark?

attributes.name: size
attributes.description:
`size` {`string`} - tiny, small, medium, large, epic sizing.

Property: size

Default: medium

attributes.name: accent-color
attributes.description:
`accent-color` {`string`} - a selected accent-"color": grey, red, pink, purple, etc.

Property: accentColor

Default: grey

attributes.name: dark
attributes.description:
`dark` {`boolean`} - make the default theme dark?

Property: dark

Default: false

attributes.name: colors
attributes.description:
`colors` - make the default theme dark?

Property: colors

Default: colors
